CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 17, 1950, pg. 7 reads: "Republicans Elect Chairman In Fifth Ward - ...The group gathered in front of the platform and comprised with Atty. Joe Givens (extreme left, leaning over the group), after he gave consent. Shown in the huddle are Attorney Givens, Lou McTurner, Lu Davenport, Clarence Jackson and the successful candidate, David Thompkins (with back to camera)."
TitMainTitle: Atty. Joe Givens, standing on stage, Lou McTurner, Lu Davenport, Clarence Jackson and David Thompkins, standing in A. Leo Weil school auditorium for Fifth Ward elections
